{"tid":867864,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 – 老娘牌足料酸辣湯","createTime":"2018-10-19T04:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T02:41:17.000Z","uid":30742,"like":60,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f101a8053e1ec640c067abd07b7cc1d2402bd5f4","tid":867864,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwR10zx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwR10zx.jpg&h=33396c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4z11cC7ibzw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4z11cC7ibzw&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d872064a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4z11cC7ibzw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q2bmAw6cwH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ2bmAw6cwH4&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4c15e635\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q2bmAw6cwH4</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我隔一排就會煮既！<br />\n因為係阿妺至愛，出面既酸辣湯多數都唔會咁多料<br />\n但我煮親都會九百幾樣料，而且一定有半個新鮮豬肚！<br />\n落左豬肚係好食勁多！<br />\n同埋一定要係新鮮豬肚，急凍完全唔會果回事！<br />\n其實洗豬肚一d都唔難，最核突都係翻開果一下，<br />\n睇完片你地就明！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <br />\n酸辣湯: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/10/hot-and-sour-soup.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fhot-and-sour-soup.html&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4333d888\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/10/hot-and-sour-soup.html</a><br />\n豬肚清洗處理: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/10/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fblog-post.html&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7689029c\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/10/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldlad